	with a space after each number in order to identify distinct numbers.....(preorder function is for this)

	now in deserializing we are storing the string into a vector(pre) and then sorting it into another
	vector (in)  now we are converting it into tree using preorder and inorder traversal
	(solve function is for this) :) */


	class Codec {
	public:
        string pre="";
